程序包 xyz.fsgik.common.net.tcp

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    FsTcpChannel
    This class represents a TCP/IP connection channel between local and remote endpoint.
    FsTcpChannelHandler<M>
    TCP/IP network channel callback handler.
    FsTcpClient
    TCP/IP client interface, client endpoint of FsTcpEndpoint.
    FsTcpClientHandler
    TCP/IP network handler for client actions.
    FsTcpEndpoint
    This interface represent an endpoint on the TCP/IP network: server or client.
    FsTcpServer
    TCP/IP server interface, server endpoint of FsTcpEndpoint.
    FsTcpServerHandler
    TCP/IP network handler in server endpoint.
  • 类概要

    FsTcpServer.Builder
